Package com.streamspin.client

Class Summary
AnswerWrapper Wraps the answer returned by the StreamSpin server
Content Models a StreamSpin update with headline and some content
ContentPopup Popup which shows the content of a StreamSpin update, which disappears if you press it again.
Friend Captures the notion of a friend in StreamSpin
Location Encapsulates a location with a name, longitude, and latitude
Profile Models an interest profile of a StreamSpin User
ServiceProfile Models a service which contains a script which can both change look and behavior of the client
StartService Models a service which has to be started manually by the user
StreamSpinClient  
StreamSpinContact Handles all the requests made to StreamSpin
UserInfo Contains all the information needed by the client at startup-/login-time.
UserMessage An overlay window showing the interface where the user can send messages to any of his friends, which are online.
XmlParser Singleton class which can parse the xml returned by various calls to StreamSpin
